{
  "stem": "3964.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were taking away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People didn't return, didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Several people tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They caught them, brought them back, killed 10 other people who had been the same barracks with them in front of everybody.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Just shot 'em.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a horrible experience and yet I counted my blessings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Emotionally, it was-- it was just almost impossible to handle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I knew I had to go on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The end of-- rather, this went on-- my position or my job went on 'til 1944, 'til about August or September 1944.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father was still with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was doing all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My sister was still with me in Kaiserwald, and she was doing OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In 1944, in September, Kaiserwald was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Russian troops were marching westward onto Riga.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I suppose the Germans didn't want to leave us behind, those who were still able to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the end of September [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were all taken out of Kaiserwald, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] including my father and my sister, put on a ship [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] out of Riga, out of the harbor of Riga, and shipped back into German-occupied territory, into Danzig.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Danzig is the capital of-- I don't know what it is today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Poland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "No, it's not Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Gdansk, to better identify it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And from there we-- we arrived in-- in Danzig or Gdansk, got off the ship, and were transported-- it's-- I'm a little vague and a little foggy there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how we were transported from the ship to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
